com.googlecode.cqengine.query.simple

Class Has<O,A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.query.simple.SimpleQuery<O,A>
      • com.googlecode.cqengine.query.simple.Has<O,A>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Query<O>

    public class Has<O,A>
extends SimpleQuery<O,A>
    Asserts that an attribute has a value (is not null).

    To accelerate has(...) queries, add a Standing Query Index on has(...).

    To assert that an attribute does not have a value (is null), use not(has(...)).

    To accelerate not(has(...)) queries, add a Standing Query Index on not(has(...)).

    Author:
    Niall Gallagher
